fi.hu.cs.titokone
Class RunInfo

java.lang.Object
  fi.hu.cs.titokone.DebugInfo
      fi.hu.cs.titokone.RunInfo
public class RunInfo
extends DebugInfo

This class tells GUIBrain and Animator what the processor has done. RunDebugger creates objects from this class and passes them onwards.
